        <heading>2297.  Obligations of the owner</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2297.  Obligations of the owner
The owner whose affair has been managed is bound to fulfill the obligations that the manager has undertaken as a prudent administrator and to reimburse the manager for all necessary and useful expenses.</p>
        </content>
